    "introduction": "Garlic toast, perfect as a substitute for crackers in a cheese platter. - \u23f2\ufe0f Prep time: 5 min - \ud83c\udf73 Cook time: 10-15 min",
    "ingredients_source_text": "- Any kind of firm, thin, sliced bread (Sourdough, Baguette) - Garlic-infused olive oil (Optionally substitute butter or regular olive oil) - Garlic salt",
